# KAIROS — copy to .env.kairos (the project's secret file; also .env works). Both are
# gitignored. Secrets ONLY via these files / env, never committed.
#
# The Phase-A backtest runs on SYNTHETIC data with no keys at all. Public venue
# funding/mark/index history (Phase B) is also keyless on Binance/Bybit REST — a key
# only buys higher rate limits or a normalized cross-venue vendor (Velo, optional).

# Optional: a data-vendor key if you wire one in scripts/get_funding.py (e.g. Velo).
# VELO_API_KEY=REPLACE-ME

# Optional override (defaults to <repo>/data/kairos in config.py)
# KAIROS_DATA_DIR=/Users/xavierbriggs/fortuna/data/kairos
